text: Dumitru Velea (born 11 February 1944) is a Romanian equestrian. He competed in the team jumping event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1944 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Romania Category:Equestrians at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bucharest
